Package: fzf
Architecture: amd64
Description: A general-purpose command-line fuzzy finder.
 fzf is a general-purpose command-line fuzzy finder. It is an interactive
 filter program for any kind of list, with support for fuzzy matching,
 preview windows, and integration with shell key bindings.
